Write the homogenize method in the NurbsSurface class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsSurface {
    homogenize() {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsSurface {
    homogenize() {
        for (let i = 0; i < this.controlPoints.length; i++) {
            for (let j = 0; j < this.controlPoints[i].length; j++) {
                this.controlPoints[i][j].push(1);
            }
        }
    }
}
```
